HealthConnectis a wearable IoT medical device powered by AVR-IoT microchip which can be wore around your arm.
It streams your health data - ECG, Heart Rate, SpO2, Body Temperature, Activity Status, Ambient Temperature over a secured AWS platform.
Real time data monitoring helps to diagnose the patient condition better in online consultation with physician.
This device can be connected to your mobile phone through HealthConnect android app, which has a feature to send SOS to your family
Doctor with a link to monitor your health data instantly. This SOS feature can helps to provide first Aid in medical emergency.
